&lt;h2 id=&#34;especial-biota-fapesphttpsrevistapesquisafapespbrentre-desafios-conceitos-e-ameacas&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://revistapesquisa.fapesp.br/entre-desafios-conceitos-e-ameacas/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Especial Biota Fapesp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
